  mySprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: d57592ae61f23a84f885d01a6df56f21, type: 3}
  OutcomeRef: 2
  myName: brass
  myDescription: "Like a tuba or a trumpet, you are bold and confident. You\u2019re
    that person that is impossible to ignore when they walk in. You thrive on attention;
    however, you\u2019re not arrogant \u2013 you radiate fearless enthusiasm others
    find magnetic. You\u2019re the friend who hypes everyone up, who volunteers first,
    who never hesitates to speak their mind. Some might say you\u2019re too much,
    but they were simply not prepared for your greatness. Instead of laying low,
    you\u2019d rather be yourself at full volume and have no regrets."
